title: Chiropractor in Willmar, MN | Renew Chiropractic
description: Renew Chiropractic provides personalized, whole body care by not only treating pain, but also the person. Call 320.403.5047!
cleaned_text: Renew Chiropractic A Whole Body Approach To Health Welcome to Renew Chiropractic! You will be welcomed by the smiling face of Lynette as you enter our office. She has been a right-hand person in the chiropractic world for 6 years. When she is not busy at the office, she enjoys spending time with her husband, children, and grandchildren. You may find her in the woods soaking in nature! Dr. Emily has been a chiropractor for 12 years and offers a variety of different techniques and therapies. She enjoys working with all age groups and is passionate about delivering WHOLE body care, not just pain focused. When she's not busy at the office, she enjoys spending time with her husband and children and playing outdoors, whether it be in the garden or out hunting.
